---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Casa dos Duques, Abiul, Pombal"
  description="Privacy policy for Casa dos Duques holiday home. Information about how we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
  canonical="/privacy/"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-8"><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-3">When you contact us through our website or booking form, we collect:</p>
    <ul class="text-slate-warm space-y-1 mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Your name</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Phone number (if provided)</li>
      <li>Preferred dates and number of guests</li>
      <li>Any other information you choose to share in your message</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-3">We use your information solely to:</p>
    <ul class="text-slate-warm space-y-1 mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Respond to your enquiries about availability and booking</li>
      <li>Process and confirm reservations</li>
      <li>Communicate essential information about your stay</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-6">We do not use your information for marketing purposes without your explicit consent.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-6">We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties except when required by law or necessary to process your booking.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-6">We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by Portuguese and EU law.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm mb-3">Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="text-slate-warm space-y-1 mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      <li>Lodge a complaint with the CNPD (Portuguese data protection authority)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-warm">For any questions about this privacy policy or to exercise your rights, contact us at <strong>fernando@casadosduques.pt</strong>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
